<p><b>Notes to Table</b><sup id="cite_ref-storecount_1-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-storecount-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<p>Partial list (stores open at end 2023, plus 4 that closed in 2012)</p>
<p>Store Type:</p>
<ul><li>F=Franchise of Dubai-based <a href="/wiki/Al_Tayer_Group" title="Al Tayer Group">Al Tayer Insignia</a></li>
<li>GL=Ground Lease - Represents store properties where Macy's was involved with the construction of the building on leased land. Macy's Inc. generally has all of the attributes of ownership of these properties for the term of the lease.</li>
<li>L=Leased - Represents store properties where Macy's Inc. leases the building and land.</li>
<li>O=Owned - Represents store properties where Macy's Inc. owns the building and land. May also include a small amount of leased premises, such as additional space, kiosk or small shop real estate.</li></ul>
